A great conversation between 
@JeffMorhous
 and 
@Wattenberger
 on The AI-Augmented Engineer about how to think about Intent.

One takeaway we keep coming back to: the unit of work isn’t a chat or a file. It’s the entire workspace. Code, context, decisions, and state all matter.

The technical layer of the agentic world is being built incredibly well. 

What's missing is the culture layer; the context, the taste, the narrative. 

I'm building that. 

